        "text": "<@U0378MDUG1Y> Thanks. I was thrilled to have stumbled across that article, because the traditional conception of \"Artificial Intelligence didn't resonate with me at all. I actually found it profoundly alienating, though I was really fortunate to have the chance to work in such an open work environment at the Strong AI Lab at the University of Auckland, where my former boss was really accepting and supportive of my divergent thinking, despite having worked in AI since the 1980s initially at Cyc and later at the IBM Watson Research Centre.",
